doc.previous: Although not recognised by the IHO treaties there are some other seas whose names have been in common use from the ancient times or in the present
doc.after: Many of these smaller seas feature in local myth and folklore and derive their names from these associations In addition to the seas a number of gulfs and straits are also recognised
